snippet.title: Let's Play GBA 0678: Nakayoshi Youchien - Sukoyaka Enji Ikusei Game (J)
snippet.description: I think it's an RPG where you play as a teacher of a kindergarten class? I don't really understand what I'm supposed to do, but it seems like the goal is to make all the kids happy or something. Well the characters are all very cute, at least.
